data.message:
Hi!
I have a problem with my main account. I cant login it on any browsers at my computer. Meanwhile I can login my FB app for iphone but I repeatedly get a message saying "Session Expired Please login again " which takes me back to the login screen. Do you have any solutions?

replies.message: Hi Hung. If you're having trouble logging into your Facebook account here are a few things to try: http://bit.ly/2rMhgLF. Please keep in mind it's against Facebook Community Standards to maintain more than one personal profile. -Brittany
